data.description: Nestled in a wonderful neighborhood, this home offers a lifestyle of comfort and beauty with timeless charm and captivating curb appeal.  The open layout invites you inside, where the living area seamlessly connects to the bright and beautiful kitchen.  The master suite is isolated with an expansive master closet. The sunroom stands as an enchanting feature, its exposed brick walls and wooden ceiling bridging indoor and outdoor living. This space invites relaxation and contemplation, bathed in sunlight and sheltered from the elements. Schedule a time to visit this beauty today!
